'''Timothée Chaillou''' is a French [[art curator]], [[art critic]] and [[History of art|historian of art]].

== Biography ==

Timothée Chaillou is a graduate of ICART,<ref name="ICART"/> of [[Paris 3|Paris III]], of [[Paris 7|Paris VII]] and of the [[City University of New York]]. He was a student of [[Vito Acconci]], [[Jacques Aumont]], [[Nicolas Bourriaud]], Jean-Luc Chalumeau and Pierre Zaoui.

He is a member of&nbsp;[[International Association of Art Critics|AICA]] (International Association of Art Critics),<ref>[http://www.aica-int.org/ AICA – International Association of Art Critics]</ref> IKT (International Association of Curators of Contemporary Art)<ref>[http://www.iktsite.org/ IKT – International Association of Curators of Contemporary Art]</ref> and CEA (Commissaires d'Exposition Associés).<ref>[http://c-e-a.asso.fr/ Commissaires d'Expositions Associés]</ref>

His exhibition reviews, essays and conversations have appeared in many catalogues, monographs and art magazines. He contributes to 20/27,<ref>[http://www.lespressesdureel.com/magazine.php?id=104 20/27, M19 éditions, Paris]</ref> Art Présence [[Art press|Artpress]], ArtUS,<ref>[http://www.artext.org/ ArtUS]</ref> Double Magazine,<ref>[http://www.lemagazinedouble.com/ Double Magazine]</ref> Dossier Journal,<ref>[http://dossierjournal.com/ Dossier Journal]</ref> ETC,<ref>[http://www.etcmontreal.com/ ETC] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130901014849/http://www.etcmontreal.com/ |date=1 September 2013 }}</ref> [[Flash Art|Flash Art International]], [[Frieze (magazine)|Frieze]], Hart,<ref>[http://www.kunsthart.org/ Hart]</ref> L'art même,<ref>[http://www2.cfwb.be/lartmeme/fram003.htm/ L'art même]</ref> L'Officiel Art,<ref>[http://www.editionsjalou.com/category/marques/lofficiel-art/ L'Officiel Art – Éditions Jalou]</ref> Numéro,<ref>[http://www.numero-magazine.com/ Numéro Magazine] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080509165449/http://www.numero-magazine.com/ |date=9 May 2008 }}</ref> [[Paddle8]] and [[The White Review]].&nbsp;He was the guest editor-in-chief of Annual Magazine No. 5<ref>[http://www.annualartmagazine.com/ Annual Magazine]</ref> in 2012.

He's an art consultant for collectors, institutions (galleries and museums), companies and luxury brands.

He is a [[lecturer]] and teaches [[Art exhibition|exhibition history]] and [[Curator|curating practices]] at IESA (Institut d’Études Supérieures d'Art)<ref name="iesa">[http://www.iesa.fr/ IESA – Institut d'Etudes Supérieures des Arts]</ref> and at ICART&nbsp;(Institut supérieur des Carrières Artistiques, Paris).<ref name="ICART">[http://www.icart.fr/ ICART – Institut Supérieur des Carrières Artistiques]</ref>

